{"prompt": "Build a personal blog about travel and adventure. The site's branding should be exciting, anchored by a cheerful yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Wanderlust & Wonder</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            background-color: #fef9e7; /* Soft, creamy background */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #ffda63; /* Cheerful yellow */\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #ffda63, #f7c948);\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            max-width: 1000px;\n        }\n        .post {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n        .post-image {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 250px;\n        }\n        .post-image img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n        .post-content {\n            flex: 2;\n            padding: 30px;\n        }\n        .post h2 {\n            color: #e6b400; /* Slightly darker yellow for emphasis */\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .post-meta {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: #888;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .post a {\n            color: #ffda63;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .post a:hover {\n            color: #e6b400;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: #ffda63;\n            color: #fff;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #fff;\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        .highlight {\n            color: #ffda63;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Wanderlust & Wonder</h1>\n        <p>Adventures from every corner of the globe.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"container\">\n        <article class=\"post\">\n            <div class=\"post-image\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/600x400/ffda63/ffffff?text=Majestic+Mountains\" alt=\"Snow-capped mountains\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"post-content\">\n                <h2>Conquering the Peaks: A Himalayan Journey</h2>\n                <div class=\"post-meta\">Posted on <span class=\"highlight\">October 26, 2023</span> by Alex</div>\n                <p>The crisp mountain air filled my lungs as I gazed upon the <span class=\"highlight\">majestic Himalayas</span>. This trek was more than just a physical challenge; it was a journey of self-discovery and awe-inspiring beauty. From prayer flags fluttering in the wind to the serene smiles of the locals, every moment was etched in my memory.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n            </div>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"post\">\n            <div class=\"post-image\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/600x400/f7c948/ffffff?text=Tropical+Paradise\" alt=\"Turquoise ocean and palm trees\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"post-content\">\n                <h2>Island Dreams: Unwinding in Zanzibar</h2>\n                <div class=\"post-meta\">Posted on <span class=\"highlight\">September 15, 2023</span> by Alex</div>\n                <p>The turquoise waters and powdery white sands of Zanzibar were a dream come true. Exploring the spice markets, swimming with dolphins, and watching the sunset over the <span class=\"highlight\">Indian Ocean</span> was pure bliss. It's a place where time seems to slow down, and worries melt away with the tide.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n            </div>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"post\">\n            <div class=\"post-image\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/600x400/ffd000/ffffff?text=Ancient+Ruins\" alt=\"Ancient stone ruins\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"post-content\">\n                <h2>Echoes of the Past: Exploring Machu Picchu</h2>\n                <div class=\"post-meta\">Posted on <span class=\"highlight\">August 01, 2023</span> by Alex</div>\n                <p>Standing amidst the ancient ruins of Machu Picchu felt surreal. The ingenuity of the Inca civilization and the breathtaking Andean scenery created an unforgettable experience. The mist rolling in and out, revealing and concealing the <span class=\"highlight\">mysterious citadel</span>, added to its allure.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n            </div>\n        </article>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Wanderlust & Wonder. All rights reserved. | Built with <a href=\"#\">passion</a> and <span class=\"highlight\">yellow</span>.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}